decision_conditions:
CONDITION : Detailed drawings or samples of materials, as appropriate, in respect of the following, shall be submitted to and approved by the Local Planning Authority before the relevant part of the work is begun:

- New stone to steps and front garden;
- Works to boundary wall to front and all railings;
- New door to rear;
- All new cornicing

REASON: In order to safeguard the special architectural or historic interest of the building included in the Statutory List.
